~ initialize_local_variables

=> start

~ start
#background: wooden gate, nearly pitch black
You're... someone. You live in a world ravaged by seemingly random occurrences known as the Cullings, events that have lead to countless gruesome deaths over the past decade. 
You're currently on your way to a village you found out about in a dream. A self-proclaimed Goddess showed Herself to you in your sleep, assuming the appearance of a crow, and told you to make your way there with haste.
You abided. Who knows why. Your reasons are your own. 
After a long and tiring trek in the dark, you finally arrive at the village gates. You can barely make someone's eyes out through what you can only assume is a sliding peephole. They watch you as you walk towards them. 
[wait=0.5]...After what feels like too long, they speak.
???: [wait=1.5]Who's there?
- I heard this village is a safe haven, untouched by hardship or the Cullings. Things are worse than ever out there. I've traveled far. I want to settle here.
	???: Not the first to ask. Sure won't be the last. Oh, Goddess, merciful, almighty and wise, what shall I do with this one? 
	???: Will he serve and praise, or will he sow discord and doubt among our ranks?
	???: [wait=1]...
	???: [wait=1.5]...Fortune smiles upon you!
	???: The Goddess is all welcoming. She's let everyone in so far, provided they're willing to leave their earthly possessions and sinful ways behind.
	???: Very soon, that won't be possible anymore. There just isn't enough space, food, or water. It saddens us all. Deeply so. 
	???: But you, you got here just in time. 
	???: And you're bearing Her Gift, are you? What a blessed day. 
	- That's... great!
		???: So it is. 
		???: She provides and cares for us. And she will provide and care for you, too. => but
	- Praise be!
		???: Praise be indeed!
		???: She provides and cares for us. And she will provide and care for you, too. => but
	- Your Goddess showed Herself to me in my sleep and told me to come here. Of course she'd let me in.
		???: The Goddess very rarely speaks to us mortals. You've been blessed. 
		???: Doubly so, since She's also bestowed Her Gift upon you. 
		???: But don't let that turn your reverence and appreciation into vanity and pride.
		???: For if there's one thing Our Blessed Goddess hates, it's arrogance. => but
	- Whatever you say. 
		???: She speaks through me. I'm a mere vessel. 
		???: She provides and cares for us. And she will provide and care for you, too. 
		???: ...In spite of your ignorant attitude. => but
	- Gift? What Gift?
		???: Don't worry about it right now. All will be revealed in due time. => but
- I heard this is the birthing place of the Church of the one true Goddess. I'd like to join. 
